# rt-extension-relocatereply

INSTALLATION:

- copy files to /usr/local/share/request-tracker4/plugins/
- copy the etc#RT_SiteConfig.d/60-RelocateReply file to /etc/request-tracker4/RT_SiteConfig.d/
- create the /usr/local/share/request-tracker4/html/Callbacks/RT-Extension-RelocateReply/ directory
- move the entire Elements directory under the created directory, thus creating the /usr/local/share/request-tracker4/html/Callbacks/RT-Extension-RelocateReply/Elements/ShowTransaction/Default file.
- run update-rt-siteconfig-4
- restart webserver to apply changes

